---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = "Privacy Policy | Pakistan Data Management Services";
const description = "Read the privacy policy for Quran Majeed, EasyUrdu, Quran TV, and other application services provided by Pakistan Data Management Services.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <section class="policy-hero">
    <div class="container text-center animate-fade-in">
      <span class="badge badge-primary">Legal Documentation</span>
      <h1 class="policy-hero-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="policy-hero-subtitle">Last Updated: May 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container max-width-800">
      <div class="policy-content card">
        <h2 class="policy-section-title">1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>
          Pakistan Data Management Services (PDMS, also referred to as "PDMS", "we", "us", or "our") respect your privacy and are committed to protecting the personal data of users who download our mobile applications (including <strong>Quran Majeed</strong>, <strong>Quran Pak</strong>, <strong>Quran TV</strong>, <strong>Easy Urdu Keyboard</strong>, and others) and visit our corporate website.
        </p>
        <p>
          This privacy policy explains how we collect, handle, use, and secure your information.
        </p>

        <h2 class="policy-section-title">2. Information Collection & Usage</h2>
        <h3 class="policy-subsection-title">A. Location Services (Quran Majeed & Quran Pak)</h3>
        <p>
          Our Islamic applications request access to your device's geographical location coordinates (GPS/Network). This permission is strictly used to compute accurate daily prayer timings and identify the correct Qibla direction relative to your location. 
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Note:</strong> Location data is processed locally on your device. We do not store or transmit your location coordinates to our servers.
        </p>

        <h3 class="policy-subsection-title">B. Microphone & Audio Access (Easy Urdu Keyboard & Quran Majeed)</h3>
        <p>
          Easy Urdu Keyboard requests microphone permission to perform voice-to-text Urdu typing transcription. Quran Majeed requests microphone permission to analyze recitation pronunciations in our learning modules.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Note:</strong> Audio recordings are processed in real time and are not recorded or saved on our servers.
        </p>

        <h3 class="policy-subsection-title">C. Payments & Billing Information</h3>
        <p>
          When you buy our Premium upgrades, payment transactions are processed securely through third-party billing services (Apple App Store, Google Play, EasyPaisa, or JazzCash). We do not collect or store credit card details or wallet PINs on our servers.
        </p>

        <h2 class="policy-section-title">3. Data Security & Storage</h2>
        <p>
          Since our applications operate primarily offline and process user data locally, we maintain a highly secure environment. Any data synchronized optionally (e.g., custom bookmarks sync via email sign-in) is encrypted in transit using SSL protocol and stored securely on cloud database systems.
        </p>

        <h2 class="policy-section-title">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>
          We may integrate trusted third-party SDKs to analyze app stability and metrics:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Google Firebase Analytics / Crashlytics:</strong> Used to monitor application performance and diagnose crashes.</li>
          <li><strong>Google AdMob:</strong> Serves non-intrusive advertisements in free app versions (users can remove advertisements via premium upgrade).</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="policy-section-title">5. Compliance & Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          Our services do not collect personal data from anyone under the age of 13. We comply with global privacy rules including the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA).
        </p>

        <h2 class="policy-section-title">6. Contact Information</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions regarding this Privacy Policy or data deletion requests, please contact our legal representative:
        </p>
        <div class="policy-contact-box">
          <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:privacy@pakdata.com">privacy@pakdata.com</a><br />
          <strong>Address:</strong> Pakistan Data Management Services, DHA Phase II Ext, Karachi, Pakistan.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .policy-hero {
    text-align: center;
    background: radial-gradient(at 20% 0%,oklch(97% .04 60) 0%,transparent 50%),radial-gradient(at 80% 20%,oklch(96% .03 220) 0%,transparent 50%),linear-gradient(180deg,oklch(99% .005 80),oklch(100% 0 0));
    padding: 4rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .policy-hero-title {
    font-size: 1.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .policy-hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--secondary-dark);
  }

  .max-width-800 {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .policy-content {
    padding: 3rem;
  }

  .policy-section-title {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 2rem 0 1rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .policy-subsection-title {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin: 1.5rem 0 0.5rem 0;
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .policy-content p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--secondary-dark);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .policy-content ul {
    margin-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--secondary-dark);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }

  .policy-content li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .policy-contact-box {
    background-color: var(--light-soft);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 1.25rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  .policy-contact-box a {
    color: var(--primary);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* Mobile: reduce card padding */
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .policy-content {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .policy-hero-title {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
